ABOUT US

Who We Are

Dominant Care Group is a service disabled veteran owned small business (SDVOSB) dedicated to providing the highest quality Veteran disability Medical examinations, Medical Opinion/Nexus Letter services, consultation services and Provider recruitment solutions.

Our mission is to provide the best services and solutions through professional excellence to Government Agencies and their clients.
